item.title: Call It Short & Sweet: That's So Nostalgic
item.description:
From layering multiple tanks to printing out a map instead of using your iPhone, Jess is flying solo and giggling her way through some submissions from the crew all about things they used to do that would make you do a triple take in 2025.
